      ],
      "source": "https://www.cocoafl.gov/908/History-Culture"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Cocoa West is part of the Palm Bay–Melbourne–Titusville Metropolitan Statistical Area, linking it to the broader Space Coast region.",
